Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:24.25,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}They're seven deadly sins
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:27.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}You feel alive when you step inside
