Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:32.22,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}綺麗事なら疾うに Break up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.87,0:02:34.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}人たらしめる罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:38.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}それはいつだって付き纏うんだ Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.51,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}死に至る罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:40.14,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}犯しても次へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:41.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}目を逸らさずに Atonement
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:42.54,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ただ前へ前へ Go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:44.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I gotta make it make it again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:45.23,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}増していく代償
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:46.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}向かう先が地獄だとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:49.69,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}後悔なんてない Anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:52.62,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Fallin' fallin' down 暗闇へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:55.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}But, never going back 立ち向かえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:57.14,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}狼煙高く上げて Now dive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:02:58.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}煩悩なんてモノ Good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.35,0:02:59.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}性懲りも無く Fight 仲間と
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:01.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Live to die another day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:04.67,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I won't run away from my sin no more
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:08.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}何処までも抗って Go on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:11.67,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今 超えていく 恐れずに Bring it on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:13.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I'm not afraid, bring it on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:16.22,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Even if I'm drown in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:19.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}自分のチカラに変え Wipe out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:21.66,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今 捻じ曲げる System
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:23.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I never follow them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:25.30,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I never ever follow them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:30.26,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今 立ち向かう and I'll defeat myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:18.34,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}就像人性一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:21.26,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你将凝视深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:24.25,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}那里有七宗罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:27.08,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}当你踏入其中 你会发觉自己还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:29.31,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}踏入未知领域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:32.22,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}那些漂亮话 早就没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.87,0:02:34.50,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}让人得以为人的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:38.08,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}总是伴随着我们 对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.51,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}致命的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:40.14,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使再犯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:41.09,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}也不要转移视线 赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:42.54,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只是向前 向前 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:44.17,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我必须再次取得成功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:45.23,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}代价在不断增加
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:46.98,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使前方是地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:49.69,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}也不再有任何后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:52.62,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}坠落 坠落 堕入黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:55.17,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}但是 永远不回头 勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:57.14,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}高举烽烟 然后潜入
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:02:58.35,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}与烦恼说再见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.35,0:02:59.97,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}惩前毖后 与伙伴一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:01.99,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}活着就是为了择日赴死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:04.67,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我不再逃避我的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:08.08,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我将一直抗争下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:11.67,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在 无畏地超越 放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:13.53,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我不害怕 放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:16.22,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使我将陷入黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:19.53,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}也要将其转化为我的力量 消除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:21.66,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在 扭曲这个系统
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:23.09,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我永远不会跟随它们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:25.30,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我永远不会跟随它们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:30.26,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在 我将面对挑战并战胜自己
